comment:
* An internal response object that prefetches user app credentials and provides metadata about
 * them.
 *
 * @hide

variables.name: mPendingIntent
variables.comment:
* The pending intent to be launched to finalize the user credential. If null, the callback
     * will fail with {@link GetCredentialException#TYPE_NO_CREDENTIAL}.

methods.name: public boolean hasCredentialResults(@NonNull String credentialType)
methods.comment:
* Returns true if the user has any candidate credentials for the given {@code credentialType},
     * and false otherwise.

methods.name: public boolean hasAuthenticationResults()
methods.comment:
* Returns true if the user has any candidate authentication actions (locked credential
     * supplier), and false otherwise.

methods.name: public boolean hasRemoteResults()
methods.comment: * Returns true if the user has any candidate remote credential results, and false otherwise.

methods.name: public void writeToParcel(@NonNull Parcel dest, int flags)

methodNames: public void writeToParcel(@NonNull Parcel dest, int flags)
